        {
            "title": "韓股初段升逾1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">南韓股市早段上升，首爾綜合指數較早時報2656點，升29點，升幅1.12%。</p>\n</div>",
