        {
            "title": "日股初段偏軟",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">日股初段偏軟，但跌幅有限。日經指數較早時報39218點，跌52點，跌幅0.13%。</p>\n</div>",
