            "title": "黑期夜期均低水逾200點 滙控ADR績前再升1.42% 百度ADR績後跌2.87%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新加坡黑期於今早約8時11分跌179點或0.78%，報22767點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股ADR指數報22789點，較香港上日現貨收市低187點或0.81%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">百度(09888)ADR於績後向下，收市折合港幣87.6元，較上日香港收市低2.59元或2.87%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合港幣501元，較上日香港收市低2.47元或0.49%；阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合港幣123.3元，較上日香港收市低2.98元或2.36%</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美團(03690)ADR收市折合港幣169.2元，較上日香港收市低3.66元或2.12%；京東(09618)ADR收市折合港幣151.2元，較上日香港收市低5.36元或3.42%；小米(01810)ADR收市折合港幣48.2元，較上日香港收市低0.25元或0.51%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：百度官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240509_FI_source-web_09888-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：百度官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240509_FI_source-web_09888-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：百度官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙控(00005)ADR收市折合港幣88.4元，較上日香港收市高1.24元或1.42%；友邦(01299)ADR收市折合港幣55元，較上日香港收市低0.42元或0.75%；港交所(00388)ADR收市折合港幣337.3元，較上日香港收市低4.09元或1.2%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合港幣46.1元，較上日香港收市低0.51元或1.1%；建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合港幣6.7元，較上日香港收市低0.06元或0.86%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指夜市期指收報22775點，跌221點，較上日恒指收市22976點，低水202點。科指期貨夜市收報5563點，較上日科指收市低水76點；國指期貨夜市收報8386點，較上日國指收市低水89點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14716289-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e5%a4%9c%e6%9c%9f%e5%9d%87%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b4%e9%80%be200%e9%bb%9e-%e6%bb%99%e6%8e%a7adr%e7%b8%be%e5%89%8d%e5%86%8d%e5%8d%871-42-%e7%99%be%e5%ba%a6adr%e7%b8%be%e5%be%8c%e8%b7%8c2-87",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/ADR-1_source-bp_-2-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-19 08:20:41",
